(6, 0, 'artists', '', 'Sergio Mega', '', '<p>Sergio Mega - DJ, producer, musician, one of the pioneers in Ukrainian electronic dance music. In the early 80&rsquo;s he began studying music at the Kiev Conservatory, his DJ-career began in the mid 90&rsquo;s under the name DJ Megabeat. In 2004 he has founded his own label CTS records. Today, more than 50 releases by Sergio Mega are available on CD, vinyl, and in digital format around the world. <br />\r\nSince 2008 Sergio Mega becomes a part of Afro Acid family. Sergio Mega and CTS Records every year present Ukraine at the international festivals of electronic music, and work in close collaboration with musicians and record labels from different countries. This experience makes possible to keep up with the latest trends and technology development areas of electronic dance music. Ukrainian artist has experience of International Dance Music Awards Official Afterparty in Miami, Dance Parade in Rotterdam, the sets in cult clubs of Amsterdam, dance floors of Goa, Jazz Koktebel Fest, and Kazantip of course.&nbsp;<br />\r\nSince&nbsp; 2009 Sergio has been a lecturer of the National Academy of Culture and Arts Managing personnel. Subject: Composition and Computer arrangement.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sergio.mega.cts\"> FACEBOOK</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/sergio-mega\">SOUNDCLOUD</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://sergiomega.com\">www.sergiomega.com</a>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Sergio Mega - DJ, пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ, пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ. пїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ 80пїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ&nbsp; пїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ, пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ&nbsp; DJ-пїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ пїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ 90пїЅ&nbsp; пїЅпїЅпїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ DJ Megabeat. пїЅ 2004пїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ&nbsp; пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ пїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅпїЅ CTS r