(23, 0, 'artists', 'no-alias', 'Niels von Geyer', '', 'DJ Niels von Geyer, Berlin, plays a mixture of progressivehouse, pumpinhouse, vocalhouse, and classix, trance, electro. Ows a studio in Berlin together with his partner Mattias Harnos. As a dance music producer, his projects are Clubmossphere, Brotherhood of Sound, Disco Hools &amp; NVG. DJ Niels von Geyer works in Hamburg, Berlin and Moscow International publications and places in different dancecharts, mixed compilation THE ANNUAL for Ministry of Sound track at CLUBBERSGUIDE TO BERLIN (Ministry of Sound)&hellip;Remix Kate Ryan &hellip;Snap. He is signed to labels of Berlin-Phenomena, Clubmossphere, Germany, CTS (UA). Participates in different venues of Germany, Europe and worldwide - Loveparade, Lovestern Galactica, DJ-Meeting, Big Bang (Sweden), etc. In his non DJ-Life he is engaged in Extravadance - Radioshow at NRJ, Weiss der Geyer radio show, Eurotops, Dancehouse, Power Vision at the central German TV (ARD/ZDF). Also known as an actor (ZDF - serial &quot;During the next maneuver ...&quot;), free author for TV (LoopTV at Viva cannel), music journalist (Dates &amp; Tendance), music editor - [030] Berlin, DJ Promotion for Ministry of Sound (Germany), Kosmo, Great Stuff Recordings, Clubland, Sony /BMG.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore information at following websites:<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/nielsvongeyer\">FACEBOOK</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.clubmossphere.de/\">www.clubmossphere.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.berlin-phenomena.de/\">www.berlin-phenomena.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.djpoolmos.clubmossphere.de/\">www.djpoolmos.clubmossphere.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.ministryofsound.de/\">www.ministryofsound.de</a><br />\r\n<br />', 'Niels von Geyer (Berlin) работает в миксе из&nbsp; стилей&nbsp;House / Minimal/ new Electro<br />\r\n<br />\r\nДеятельность продюсера:<br />\r\nСобственная студия в Берл