(29, 0, 'artists', 'no-alias', 'Storm Tarrion', '', 'Storm Tarrion spawned from a troubled past growing up on the streets of Sydney Australia, you might say that his history led him to this point in time&hellip;. Music has always been a major part of his life, the most constant, it`s his driving passion. For the past ten years Adonaiiis has been writing heavily and composing original music in many forms. His style is unique and unlike any other, there are hints of rock, acid, electronic pop and old school house. The basis of his concept is to inspire the imagination and to make people listen a little closer, as there are many layers to his music. Storm understands that what is real and what is imagined is the same thing&hellip;.. After growing popularity, interest on the internet and some collaboration with other artists, now Storm already find a place to call home and to take things to a higher level - this is CTS records. <br />', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '', '', './../images/29_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:52:46', '2009-03-30', 'yes', 'no', 7, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
