;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\\\"Times New Roman\\\";\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->\r\n<p text-indent:=\"\" style=\"\" class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">CTS Records presents fresh vinyl by Sergio Mega - &laquo;Only friends&raquo;. This release includes remix from DJ Pierre (USA). DJ Pierre is a legendary &ldquo;acid &ndash; house&rdquo; style founder. In 1986 acid sound was created, and in August 2007 &ndash; the world celebrated its 20&rsquo;s anniversary. Not many artists in history of the dance music can boast of such list of admirers as Carl Cox, X-press 2, Junior Vasquez, Danny Tenaglia, Michael Mayer, Tom Stephan...<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">&quot;I feel the regenerated sense of this style in my career. I have never had so many positive emotions which I get now. I assign enough time to create and play music that I love&rdquo; &ndash; DJ Pierre says.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"><b><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">&ldquo;you never stop amazing me&rdquo;- fr</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">ea</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">k and s</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">y</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">nt</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">h</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">&ndash;pop singer from Australia &ndash; Storm Tarrion</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">, </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">the participant of &laquo;Only friends&raquo; project </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">say</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">s</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">.</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> Collaboration of Storm Tarrion with Sergio Mega </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">and </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">CTS</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> label</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">began in 2005 and </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">has been</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> proceed</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">ing</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">now.</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">The start of their collaboration was </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">the danc</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">e</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> hit of 2005 </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">called</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> &ldquo;Trust me&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">,</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> where vocal part was </span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">performed</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> by Storm</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\"> Tarrion</span><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"><span lang=\"\\&quot;UK\\&quot;\" style=\"\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"><span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\">A few reviews about the &laquo;Only friends&raquo; release from the professionals of music ind