ze: 14pt;\">Tape Masters</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"> is the project of famous DJ DerBastler and DJ Ingvo who is well known by his keyboards and creative work in &ldquo;Stereolisa&rdquo; crew, starts at CTS records with their <i style=\"\">minimal techno</i> stomper &ldquo;In Minimal&rdquo;&hellip; <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 35.4pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Actifish</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"> &ndash; new artist signed at CTS records and his brilliant <i style=\"\">techno</i> beats &ldquo;Clowns&rdquo; will force everybody dance&hellip;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Hypnotic<i style=\"\"> deep techno </i>sounds by <b style=\"\">Lamineylf</b> are touching your consciousness&hellip; project concept is combination of contemporary tech music and all the wide spectrum of wild nature grooves&hellip;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: blue;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">ENJOY&hellip;<span style=\"\">&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>', NULL, 'Techno EP release at CTS records! 3 new outstanding techno tracks, by Ukrainian artists are rocking the dance floors of all over the world this summer. ', NULL, './../images/104_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2009-04-08 13:00:25', '2009-04-01', 'yes', 'no', 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(105, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'DJ Small feat. Rhythm Fest – The Dust', NULL, 'New release by famous Ukrainian DJ &amp; artist &ndash; DJ Small.  <br />\r\nMove to the rhythm, feel the vibe of live tribes and powerful energy of Drumma Dub mix and massive techno sounds of Sergio Mega&rsquo;s remix. <br />\r\nNow DJ Small works a lot with winner of Eurovision &ndash; Ruslana from Ukraine, making remixes and sounds for project Ruslana Clubin and also her stage live performances.<br />\r\nPrerelease is out now at www.beatport.com  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFew reviews about the release:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGreg Desty (Various mtl., Canada):<br />\r\n&ldquo;Exelent! Will chart bouth mixes&rdquo;<br />\r\ncharting - YES<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSound Within Motion (Canada)<br />\r\n&ldquo;love the vocal samples. It flows very well&rdquo;<br />\r\ncharting - YES<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSylvin Wood (&ldquo;Tea light&rdquo;, France)<br />\r\n&ldquo;pas mal&rdquo;<br />\r\ncharting - YES<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJokton Strealy (Pocket Underground, Vanguard, USA)<br />\r\n&ldquo;interesting&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStreamteck (Kiss FM; Ukraine)<br />\r\n&ldquo;Good job! Massive tech sounds&rdquo;<br />', NULL, 'CTS Records new release:\r\nDJ Small feat. Rhythm Fest – The Dust\r\n', NULL, './../images/105_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:53:55', '2009-04-02', 'yes', 'no', 20, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(106, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Sergio Mega - The Fest', NULL, 'New bomb by Sergio Mega!!!<br />\r\nPumping Techno original mix makes to move and roll and nothing can&rsquo;t stop this feeling at the dancefloor&hellip; Feel the vibe of Electro and prog mix by Andrea Martini (Emotive Sounds)&hellip; Dance with Electric sounds of Aquabeat remix&hellip;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFEEL GOOD VIBE &amp; ENJOY<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />', NULL, 'CTS Records new release:\r\nSergio Mega - The Fest\r\n', NULL, './../images/106_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2009-04-08 13:00:25', '2009-04-02', 'yes', 'no', 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
