(107, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Aquabeat - Chernobyl', NULL, 'From Ukraine with love!!!<br />\r\nCTS records presents new release by Aquabeat, remixed by united DJs from Ukrainian labels. Feel radioactive powerful sound and pumping beats, directly for club scene. Tracks from this release are already supported by many DJs around the globe, few reviews about the release:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;good electro from Ukrainian guys&rdquo; <br />\r\nWebmen (USA) about Original mix<br />\r\n&ldquo;cool beat thanks will look forward to whole ep .. Crisp production, thanks&rdquo; <br />\r\nDJ Think (Fresh FM , Visionz Festival, New Zealand) about Original mix<br />\r\n&ldquo;I love it!&rdquo; <br />\r\nWebmen (USA) about remix by Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde<br />\r\n&ldquo;sweet and driving sort of track that works good to rock a house&rdquo;<br />\r\nAriel Cybana about remix by Andi Wax<br />\r\n&ldquo;best mix for this track! Andi Rulezzz&rdquo;<br />\r\nWebmen about remix by Andi Wax<br />\r\n&ldquo;funky with all the solid elements&rdquo;<br />\r\nLee Bradley about radio mix by Andi Wax<br />\r\n&ldquo;charting it&rdquo;<br />\r\nNoel Sanger (Dissident Music, Armada, Baroque, Curve, USA) about Original mix<br />\r\n&ldquo;cool&rdquo;<br />\r\nJokton Strealy (Pocket Underground, Vanguard, USA) about remix by Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde<br />\r\n&ldquo;Nice tech sound&rdquo;<br />\r\nWebmen about remix by Vincent Rio &amp; Vladimir Great<br />\r\n<br />\r\nENJOY &amp; don&rsquo;t forget to check your dosimeter ;)<br />\r\n<br />', NULL, 'CTS Records new release:\r\nAquabeat - Chernobyl\r\n', NULL, './../images/107_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2009-04-08 13:00:25', '2009-04-02', 'yes', 'no', 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
