(117, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Sergio Mega @ Proton Radio', NULL, 'Listen to<br />\r\nSergio Mega special mix on Proton Radio<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn show Galilieo of DJ Onirika &ndash;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.protonradio.com/show.php?showid=262\">www.protonradio.com/show.php</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvery Monday Niels von Geyer, the Ministry Of Sound (Berlin) resident, presents the brand-new and the hottest tracks from the world of electronic music. Sunshine Live Radio and Ministry Of Sound cooperation has created a perfect platform for high-quality dance music from the whole world. Every Monday evening Niels von Geyer presents in his two-hour show the best House, Electro and Progressive sounds. Every week exclusive DJ mix from famous artists such as David Guetta, Bob Sinclar, Stonebrige, Eric Pridz, Mousse T and many others go on the air! <br />\r\nRadio show from Ministry of Sound is an acoustic firework of superior-quality! <br />\r\nMonday, February 2,<br />\r\n22.00 - 23.00 (Kiev time)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTracklist:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1.	Cobblestone Jazz &ndash; Dump Truck (Original mix) Wagon Repair / K7 Records<br />\r\n2.	Tape Masters &ndash; In Minimal (Original mix), CTS Records<br />\r\n3.	Booka Shade &ndash; City Tales (Neon Dub) Get Physical Music<br />\r\n4.	Shiz &ndash; Insomnia (Sergio Mega remix) CTS Records<br />\r\n5.	Ame &ndash; Rej (Pastaboys dub mix) Defected Records<br />\r\n6.	Julian Jeweil &ndash; Air Conditionne (Original mix) Skryptom Records<br />\r\n7.	Marc Romboy vs Stephan Bodzin &ndash; Hyperion (Original mix) Systematic<br />\r\n8.	Sergio Mega &ndash; Be yourself (M.I.D.I. phobia mix) CTS Records<br />\r\n9.	Deb feat. MC Yug &ndash; Plastic Toys (Original mix) CTS Records<br />\r\n10.	Oliver Koletzki &ndash; Da Bleibt Er Ganz Cool (Original mix) Kling Klong Records<br />\r\n11.	Sergio Mega &ndash; System one (Original mix) CTS Records / The Source<br />\r\n<img height=\"98\" width=\"175\" src=\"/images/C.gif\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <img height=\"136\" width=\"125\" src=\"/images/SM.gif\" alt=\"\" /><br />', NULL, 'Sergio Mega on Proton Radio\r\n19 of September 2008\r\n', NULL, './../images/117_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 14:35:31', '2009-04-03', 'yes', 'no', 11, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(118, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Creative EP vol. 6', NULL, 'CTS records continue edition of digital compilations releases, for your attention CTS Creative EP vol.6 in Electro-House style. This compilation will make happy non vocal mixes lovers, outstanding dub mix of track by Sergio Mega featuring MC Yug &ndash; &ldquo;Funk, Flight, Magic&rdquo; already got massive support from DJs worldwide; Ukrainian DJ &amp; producer Ekspert makes debut on CTS records with explosive track &ldquo;Meat on the Dancefloor&rdquo;; new CTS artists from Argentina project D-geetals start their musical trip with track &ldquo;Mute Symphony&rdquo; melodic &amp; cool&hellip;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFew DJ comments about the release:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;banging bomb!&rdquo;<br />\r\nDJ Mindaugelis (Audio Therapy, Lithuania) about Sergio Mega feat. MC Yug &ndash; &ldquo;Funk, Flight, Magic&rdquo; (Dub mix)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;bomb&rdquo;<br />\r\nWebmen (USA) about Sergio Mega feat. MC Yug &ndash; &ldquo;Funk, Flight, Magic&rdquo; (Dub mix)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Very interesting synth editing, love the squelch&rdquo;<br />\r\nAnonymo (Milano\'s, Canada) about Sergio Mega feat. MC Yug &ndash; &ldquo;Funk, Flight, Magic&rdquo; (Dub mix)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;cool&rdquo;<br />\r\nJokton Strealy (Pocket Underground, Vanguard, Avalon, USA) about Ekspert &ndash; &ldquo;Meat on the dancefloor&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;very good&rdquo;<br />\r\nGreg Desty (Various Mtl., Canada) about Ekspert &ndash; &ldquo;Meat on the dancefloor&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;has a good melody and a good job on the mix&rdquo;<br />\r\nAriel Cybana (Digitally Imported/365 Magazine, San Francisco, USA) about D-geetals &ndash; &ldquo;Mute symphony&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;good bassline, uplift&amp;tide groove, nice one&rdquo;<br />\r\nDJ Hano (BOUNENKAI, Exotica, Japan) about D-geetals &ndash; &ldquo;Mute symphony&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;very good&rdquo;<br />\r\nGreg Desty (Various Mtl., Canada) about D-geetals &ndash; &ldquo;Mute symphony&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nENJOY&hellip;<br />\r\n<br />', NULL, 'CTS records new release\r\nCreative EP vol. 6\r\n', NULL, './../images/118_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:52:46', '2009-04-03', 'yes', 'no', 7, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
