(122, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Sergio Mega – Not You', NULL, 'Another big release by Sergio Mega. Combination of Electro-House and Techno sounds. <br />\r\n3 tracks from the release reached top 50 of Releasepromo.com. Feel Electro &amp; House magic vibes of Extended club mix and Ekspert remix. Like Techno?... Take Actifish mix, for Progressive party Michael Ruby remix better choice. Would like to add Electro &amp; Tech colors to your mix?... Rock it with Aquabeat remix. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDJs reactions:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Wow! What a slammin big-room system rattler! People are going to LLLLLUUUUUVVVVV this mix! Excellent, will chart&rdquo;<br />\r\nDave Brock (Daybreak Heavyweights, Cicadia Rhythm (Jacksonville, FL, USA)) <br />\r\nabout Extended Club mix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Very good, will chart&rdquo;<br />\r\nGreg Desty (Various Mtl., Canada) about remix by Michael Ruby<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;nice rhythm and a kinda slammin groove with the awesome synthline&rdquo;<br />\r\nAriel Cybana (Digitally Imported/365 Magazine (San Francisco, USA))<br />\r\nabout Extended Club mix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Tight mix here as well - has a decidedly more banging edge to it&rdquo;<br />\r\nDave Brock (Daybreak Heavyweights, Cicadia Rhythm (Jacksonville, FL, USA)) <br />\r\nabout remix by Michael Ruby<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Very good,  charting - YES&rdquo;<br />\r\nGreg Desty (Various Mtl., Canada) about Extended Club mix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;great progressive electro track&rdquo;<br />\r\nJason Valentino (Special Events Manager/Vip Manager Nikki Beach)<br />\r\nAbout Ekspert remix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;GOOD&rdquo;<br />\r\nWebmen (Webmensuor, (WA), USA) about Ekspert remix<br />\r\n&ldquo;Nice build up to a slow and intense drop, will chart&rdquo;<br />\r\nAnonymo (Milano&rsquo;s, Canada) about Extended Club mix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Super next-generation disco vibe bouncing through this tasty treat for any floor. Supremely funky! Charting - YES&rdquo;<br />\r\nDave Brock (Daybreak Heavyweights, Cicadia Rhythm (Jacksonville, FL, USA)) <br />\r\nabout remix by Ekspert<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;love glichy vocal tracks dude. not to mention, the bass is hypnotic, excellent, charting - YES&rdquo;<br />\r\nSound Within Motion (Canada) about Ekspert remix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Very good, charting &ndash; YES&rdquo;<br />\r\nGreg Desty (Various Mtl., Canada) about remix by Ekspert<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Nice build up&rdquo;<br />\r\nAnonymo (Milano&rsquo;s, Canada) about Aquabeat remix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Oooh this is a nasty beast of a track - raw, thumping, gnarly&rdquo;<br />\r\nDave Brock (Daybreak Heavyweights, Cicadia Rhythm (Jacksonville, FL, USA)) <br />\r\nabout remix by Aquabeat<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;has a cool bassline of sorts and some nice twisted sounds to it&rdquo;<br />\r\nAriel Cybana (Digitally Imported/365 Magazine (San Francisco, USA))<br />\r\nabout Aquabeat remix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Very good, charting &ndash; YES&rdquo;<br />\r\nGreg Desty (Various Mtl., Canada) about remix by Actifish<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;good solid track. has a nice kickdrum and groove to it as well with the effected vocals&rdquo;<br />\r\nAriel Cybana (Digitally Imported/365 Magazine (San Francisco, USA))<br />\r\nabout Actifish remix<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />', NULL, 'CTS Records presents \r\nSergio Mega – Not You\r\n', NULL, './../images/122_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 14:35:31', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(123, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', '2Sleepy – Turn back', NULL, '<br />\r\n2sleepy Ukraine based indie tronic team. The story of &laquo;2sleepy&raquo; commences at the end of 2005 when two friends: Andriy \'Paranoid\' (drum-machine, programming, vocal), and Yura \'Dorialan\' (guitar, keyboard, back vocal) decided to combine their efforts in order to compose music and share it via the Internet. Then they meet Seva Solncev (vocal, keyboards, programming) who joined the band. Initially, their music was heavily influenced by Bjork and NIN. Band&rsquo;s name was inspired by the incidental phrase &ldquo;&hellip;not now, I&rsquo;m too sleepy&rdquo;. &ldquo;2sleepy&rdquo; used Internet to share their music and thus gained support among Ukrainian (and foreign) audiences. CTS records presents &ldquo;Turn Back&rdquo; by 2Sleepy, including Original mix,  remixes by Sergio Mega and Dunaewsky 69. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy&hellip;<br />\r\n<br />', NULL, 'CTS Records new release\r\n2Sleepy – Turn back\r\n', NULL, './../images/123_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 14:33:17', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 16, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
