 The release of Ikiro includes three tracks &ndash; &laquo;Nirvana&raquo;, with an east colour, in the rhythms of Progressive House. &laquo;Cube&raquo; and &laquo;Flight&raquo; balance between House and Electro. Electro-house still is one of the most claimed directions in dance music.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img height=\"200\" width=\"200\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Ikiro-ep-(500).jpg\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</meta>\r\n</meta>\r\n</meta>\r\n</meta>', NULL, 'CTS Records presents\r\nDeb EP & Ikiro EP\r\n', NULL, './../images/125_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 14:33:45', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 15, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(126, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'AQUABEAT - Aggressor', NULL, 'CTS Records presents new single release by Aquabeat project &ndash; &ldquo;Aggressor&rdquo;. All remixes in this release are filled with energetic, driving, club sound. Electro-house Ekspert remix&rsquo;s been created in French style, electrified remixes from Tarska and ZHYVO will carry your consciousness on the dancefloor. The Techno lovers will get in the record collection Actifish remix, massive sound of this mix is good for rave and evening-parties in an underground club&hellip; Techno Reedit &ndash; this is Techno &amp; Electro plus a bit House &ndash; it&rsquo;s more universal and will suit as large dancefloor so private party in a little club. We will remind that the original version of &ldquo;Aggressor&rdquo; was quite recently published in compilation of label The Source from the USA.<br />', NULL, 'CTS Records New Release\r\nAQUABEAT - Aggressor\r\n', NULL, './../images/126_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 14:30:24', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 17, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(127, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Kotov & Andre Wilde – Mini Human Beings', NULL, 'Here is a new release from the Canadian DJ duo Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde. The tints of Techno and House are interlaced in this release. Resilient and dense sound of an original mix harmonizes with Powerful Minimal remix by Sergio Mega. There&rsquo;s high-quality Techno music from Toronto from Joee Cons  &ndash; who is the resident of The Guvernment Club. Joee Cons Insomnia remix &ndash; you couldn&rsquo;t fell asleep&hellip;. A juicy remix from Michael Ruby who is the resident of CTS completes this release.<br />', NULL, 'CTS Records new release\r\nKotov & Andre Wilde – Mini Human Beings\r\n', NULL, './../images/127_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:51:58', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 22, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(128, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'DJ Pierre (USA) on December, 12th in Cinema club', NULL, '<img height=\"425\" width=\"300\" src=\"/images/chicago_a3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\nAn Acid House pioneer, who is an author of the first track in Acid style &ndash; DJ Pierre from Chicago is playing his special set in Kiev on the first party from the series of &laquo;Ctsound&raquo;. Not many artists in history of the dance music can boast of such admirers as Carl Cox, Junior Vasquez, Danny Tenaglia, X-press 2, Michael Mayer, Tom Stephan.<br />\r\nFelix Da Housecat, who has received Grammy award twice, often reminisces the first experience behind the DJ board which he owes again all the same DJ Pierre. Since 1986 DJ Pierre&rsquo;s unscrewed the handles of epochal synthesizer of TV 303 in own Acid style and has created famous Acid Trax, the great number of his releases went out on labels: like Strictly Rhythm, Jive, Emotive, Nervous, Twisted, Ovum, King Street, and Defected.<br />\r\nAlso now DJ Pierre successfully co-operates with Ukrainian independent label CTS Records on which a vinyl with his participation was published and on invitation of which he&rsquo;s arriving to Kiev for this time. The freshest work by DJ Pierre is a release named &laquo;I\'\'ve Lost Control&raquo; released on label DJ Hell &ndash; Gigolo Records. A release on vinyl started on November, 14, in a digital format it will be accessible from 26th of November. &laquo;I\'\'ve Lost Control&raquo; have been already supported by Laurent Garnier, Ame, Radio Slave, Phonique, Shinedoe, D\'\'julz, Alex Smoke. For the party in Cinema club DJ Pierre&rsquo;s prepared for Kiev clubbers special Afro Acid set from selected Techno, Tech-house and Minimal certainly with the colour of Acid. In the line-up of the first party from the series of &bdquo;Ctsound&rdquo; except DJ Pierre also are announced: residents of CTS Records<br />\r\nSergio Mega,http://www.myspace.com/sergiomega <br />\r\nDJ DerBastler,http://www.myspace.com/tapemastersua <br />\r\nEkspert (Live),http://www.myspace.com/djekspert <br />\r\nActifish, http://www.myspace.com/actifish <br />\r\nAquabeat dj\'s http://www.myspace.com/aquabeatdjs <br />\r\n<br />\r\nresidents of Cinema club -   <br />\r\nDJ Yoshi, http://djyoshi.promodj.ru/   <br />\r\nTina Valen,http://www.myspace.com/tinavalen <br />\r\nLoyva http://www.myspace.com/loyva<br />\r\n<br />', NULL, 'Legendary creator of Acid style – DJ Pierre (USA) on December, 12th in Cinema club', NULL, './../images/128_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2009-04-08 13:00:25', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 18, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(129, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'SERGIO MEGA «1 Week in Amsterdam»', 'SERGIO MEGA «1 Week in Amsterdam»', '<img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/1Week(200)part1.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe brand-new release from the CTS Records founder  --  Sergio Mega consists of two parts.<br />\r\nPumping techno sound of the Original mix becomes intertwined with Electro-House French-styled remix from DJ Ekspert.  Techno remix from CTS Records resident  -- Michael Ruby, who is also resident of KISS FM radiostation, completes the first part of &quot;Amsterdam trip&quot;.<br />\r\nThe second part of the release includes three remixes from American continent. The first is special Dubtro at the Melkweg remix from American DJ and producer -- Vinny Fiore. This New York DJ, who is fascinated with cult club Melkweg has stated his fresh impressions of Amsterdam in his Progressive remix.<br />\r\nAlso there are other two versions of the track &quot;1 Week in Amsterdam&quot; . Canadian residents of the CTS Records Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde were working hard for this project and as a result they present two remixes -- Tech-House-styled White Widow mix and Techno-styled Black Widow mix. Enjoy... <br />\r\nSergio Mega &quot;1 Week In Amsterdam&quot; Beatport Featured Minimal Release:<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.beatport.com/en-US/html/content/genre/detail/14/Minimal\">www.beatport.com/en-US/html/content/genre/detail/14/Minimal</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/1Week(200)part2.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<br />', 'Н', 'CTS Records new release: \r\nSERGIO MEGA\r\n«1 Week in Amsterdam»\r\n', 'SERGIO MEGA «1 Week in Amsterdam»', './../images/129_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:52:21', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 21, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(130, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'TAPE MASTERS «In Minimal» REMIXED', 'TAPE MASTERS «In Minimal» REMIXED', 'The long-expected original release from international DJ-duo Tape Masters - &quot;In Minimal&quot; has been released as a part of compilation CTS EP (techno edition). From that time CTS Records label has received a lot of requests from DJs and party people asking when the new release is coming...   <br />\r\nTape Masters a.k.a DJ Ingvo and DJ DerBastler are working hard for their new projects. Serbian DJ and producer DJ Ingvo is on his USA tour now and DJ DerBastler, who is the one of Ukrainian electronic dance floor founders, is busy in Kyiv clubs...<br />\r\nIn spite of the distance which separates this creative alliance duet continues their joint work. And DJ-duet has prepared for listeners their release &quot;In Minimal&quot; in remixes. Club Techno remix with Minimal elements from Sergio Mega and Tech-House and a little bit electro remix from Aquabeat DJs. The third ending remix in this release is Deep Techno version from Lamineylf, a new project of famous Ukrainian electronic master Dunaewsky 69. This track is full of sounds from wild nature. Perhaps, whales whose calls also have been intertwined in this remix, couldn\'t hear clubber\'s screams from the dance floor but only if they screamed loud enough...<br />\r\nTape Masters -- &quot;In Minimal&quot;... Enjoy...<br />\r\n<br />', 'Д', 'CTS Records new release:\r\nTAPE MASTERS\r\n«In Minimal»\r\nREMIXED\r\n', 'TAPE MASTERS «In Minimal» REMIXED', './../images/130_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:49:14', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 24, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(131, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'FRESH & MAJESTIC EP', 'FRESH & MAJESTIC EP', 'From Russia with House, new release from Russian residents of Ukrainian imprint &ndash; CTS Records. Fresh &amp; Majestic &ndash; duo of well known DJs and producers from St Petersburg famous by their musical creativity in fashion sphere. This EP is one more work by DJ Fresh who already takes part in two projects signed to CTS records. One of them is Sambooca; their House tracks are played by many famous DJs as Sultan, DJ Tarkan, The Mystic Force etc. Partner of DJ Fresh in Sambooca project &ndash; Oleg Korovin already have a releases at one of the most famous house label in industry &ndash; Head Kandi, makes tracks with Funky Junction and have strong support of Rodger Sanchez and David Vendetta.  Second crew of DJ Fresh at CTS is Sketch Of Groove, Chill Out &amp; Downtempo live band. Digital EP by Fresh &amp; Majestic combines best features of both previous projects and reflects club &amp; house colors of modern Russian fashion podium. &ldquo;Funky House&rdquo; and &ldquo;Jazzy&rdquo; is a choice of DJ DerBastler for mixed CD release &ldquo;Beatitude lounge collection&rdquo;, which also includes tracks by Caf&eacute; Del Mar compilation participant Omaya. <br />', 'F', 'CTS Records presents\r\nFRESH & MAJESTIC EP\r\n', 'CTS Records представляет FRESH & MAJESTIC EP', './../images/131_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 14:33:36', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 13, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(132, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CTSound EP volume 2 Chill Out Edition', 'CTSound EP volume 2 Chill Out Edition', 'Feel the pastel colored sounds and the ocean beach moods of CTSound EP Chill Out Edition. Release includes Downtempo Lounge composition by famous Ukrainian composer Tka4. His musical contribution to Ukrainian Pop culture is really giant (big). Sea breathed track &ldquo;Weird Creations&rdquo; by Tka4 will suit to any Lounge party. EP combines different sides of Chill Out stream from Ambient by Ikiro to Chill Breaks debut track by DJ YuraBest and Experimental electronic grooves by project of well known DJ DerBastler, Futura Partitura vs Foa Hoka. Chill Out Edition of CTSound EP will be a bright part of PRE Party DJ palette. <br />', 'П', 'CTS Records new release\r\nCTSound EP volume 2\r\nChill Out Edition\r\n', 'CTSound EP volume 2 Chill Out Edition', './../images/132_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:47:52', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 25, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
