(133, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CINEMA club presents series of parties \"Label VS Label\"  CTSound VS Innerspace', NULL, '<img height=\"505\" width=\"330\" src=\"/images/baner_special.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOn the 7th of March in CINEMA club, which is considered as the stronghold of Ukrainian underground, two Kiev imprints will meet. For both labels in the base of work lies creation of their own author musical product. Label Ctsound, which is Ukrainian home for the legend of Acid House &ndash; DJ Pierre, is known for dance music fans as the CTS brand, was founded in spring of 2005th by DJ and producer Sergio Mega a.k.a. DJ Megabeat.<br />\r\nThe management of Innerspace label, which is being based on rich Techno traditions of Cinema club, has taken upon himself veteran of Ukrainian dancefloor - DJ Yoshi together with one of the label founders &ndash; DJ Udjin. Ctsound creates wide spectrum of music from House and Electro to different directions of Techno and IDM, it is united by innovations and demand for it on the world dancefloors. Innerspace presents dance music in the genres of Deep-house, Techno, Minimal and IDM.<br />\r\nPhilosophy of musicians-residents of the both labels is directed on creative steps in area of development of the Ukrainian dance culture inalienable part of which is high-quality author electronic music. Participants in the sets will present for the guests of this party the newest dance tracks. One of the founders of Ukrainian DJ stage, Ctsound resident &ndash; DJ Derbastler will present the new combined project with the Serbian musician and sound-producer DJ Ingvo. For the Serbian artist this will be the first party after long tour in the USA. Lathe Speaks &ndash; the project of Eugen Makhno (DJ Udjin) and Dmitry Levchenko (Tweedo) will present for clubbers the fresh material. First release by Lathe Speaks &laquo;Good morning st. Monica EP&raquo; is planned in May, 2009. Rey-na and Michael Ruby, who are well known by the listeners of Kiss FM, also are participants in projects of Ctsound label. Release by Sergio Mega &ndash; &ldquo;1 Week in Amsterdam&rdquo;, which includes Michael Ruby&rsquo;s remix, has got status of Beatport Featured Minimal Release. Combined work of Rey-na with Aquabeat project will be released on CTS in the spring of 2009th. Lady Deep of Ukrainian dancefloor &ndash; Tina Valen and Acid romanticism Pionist will show their skills. The first release by Pionist went out on Innerspace label and was named &ldquo;White depth EP&rdquo;. Single &ldquo;Slow Love&rdquo; from Actifish will be the next release by Techno producer on CTS label. His joint works with his partner Aggressor are highly apprised and claimed among Ukrainian techno fans, similarly as well as spatial Groove in author works of Innerspace resident &ndash; Damaskin.<br />', NULL, 'CINEMA club presents series of parties \"Label VS Label\"\r\n\r\nCTSound VS Innerspace\r\n', NULL, './../images/133_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:49:14', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 23, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(134, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CTSound vs Innerspace. Postannounce', 'CTSound vs Innerspace. Постанонс', 'On the 7th of March the party called CTSound VS Innerspace passed in Cinema Club. Two Ukrainian labels have presented for their audience the newest tracks in the stirring DJ sets. <br />\r\nTHANK YOU for coming to support CTSound and Innerspace!!! <br />\r\nPhotos from the party you can watch and get here:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://nightlife.ua/gallery/cat/1402/\">nightlife.ua/gallery/cat/1402/</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nVideo:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8DX4QU4Lid8\">www.youtube.com/watch</a><br />\r\n<br />', '7', 'CTSound vs Innerspace. Postannounce', 'CTSound vs Innerspace. Постанонс', './../images/134_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:41:33', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 29, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(135, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Aquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Cocaine', 'Aquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Cocaine', 'New powerful single release from CTS residents -- Aquabeat. Different sides of Techno, Electro, House, and vocal part by voice of Kiss FM (Ukraine) - Rey-Na are combined in this edition. Natural musical energizer by Aquabeat includes original version made in Electro-House, remix by Michael Ruby in Tech &amp; Minimal. Non standard bass forms of Vein Litterback\'s remix takes you into the Progressive, Tech-House ride. Release is festooned by Techno remix from well known Brasilian DJ &amp; producer -- Truati.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRelease is already in Beatport top 100 downloads.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Н', 'Aquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Cocaine\r\n', 'Aquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Cocaine', './../images/135_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:47:17', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 26, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(136, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CTSound EP volume 3', 'CTSound EP volume 3', '<span lang=\"\\&quot;EN-US\\&quot;\" style=\"\"><font face=\"\\&quot;Arial\\&quot;\"><font size=\"\\&quot;2\\&quot;\"><span font-family:=\"\" style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"><font color=\"#00f4f0\"><font color=\"#00f4f0\"><font color=\"#000000\">After Chill Out edition, CTSound EP vol.3 is made for dancefloor. Release consists of Progressive &amp; Electro House sounds. Russia based Sambooca also known as DJ Fresh &amp; Korovin with their track &quot;Coming Hard&quot;. Sicilian resident of CTS Records -- Marcello Mineo remixed by DJ Small. &quot;Golden&quot; new Electro House burner by Aquabeat and &quot;Sky Rose&quot; Tech-House and Progressive debut track on CTS by Daniel Ost. Enjoy...</font></font></font></span></span></font></font></span>', 'П', 'CTSound EP volume 3\r\n', 'CTSound EP volume 3', './../images/136_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:30:47', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 32, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(137, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'New A&R (Russia) on CTS Records ', 'New A&R (Russia) on CTS Records ', '<span style=\"font-size: small;\">We are glad to announce new A&amp;R on CTS Records. Many people from Russia are sending their productions to CTS, that is why we decide to get better connection with Russian DJ\'s and producers. We present DJ Fresh at CTS Records. Russian DJ &amp; producer Roma Fresh is regular participant of CTS events and releases. Sambooca with Oleg Korovin, Fresh &amp; Majestic, Sketch Of Groove just to name a few...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo if you live in Russia and like to get released on CTS, from now feel free to contact our A&amp;R -- DJ Roma Fresh via e-mail: <a href=\"javascript:location.href=\'mailto:\'+String.fromCharCode(114,111,109,97,95,102,114,101,115,104,64,99,116,115,45,115,116,117,100,105,111,46,99,111,109)+\'?\'\">roma_fresh@cts-studio.com</a></span>', 'М', 'New A&R (Russia) on CTS Records \r\n', 'New A&R (Russia) on CTS Records ', './../images/137_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:34:41', '2009-04-08', 'yes', 'no', 31, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
