(274, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Sergio Mega - Stereoland', 'Sergio Mega - Stereoland', 'CTS Records presents new single release by Sergio Mega. &ldquo;Stereoland&rdquo; is front track of Mega&rsquo;s double CD album &ldquo;Stereo&rdquo;. This project was granted by fond of Victor Pinchuk &amp; Arseny Yatsenuk &ldquo;Open Ukraine&rdquo; for the Ukrainian Arts forwarding to an International society. &ldquo;Stereoland&rdquo; combines authentic and innovative genres of Ukrainian musical arts. National festive songs performed by Astarta and Lady Taka, unique melodic part on authentic Ukrainian flute performed by Alexander Radion meet Sergio Mega&rsquo;s modern Tech-House rhythms, really explosive mixture.  Minimal-Techno remix by Canadian residents of CTS Records, Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde and Techno version by Andi Vax will burn any dacefloor. For Electro-House sounds lovers will pass remix by CTS newcomer Daniel Ost. <br />\r\nStereoland Video coming SOON&hellip;<br />\r\n<br />', 'C', 'CTS Records presents new single release by Sergio Mega. “Stereoland” is front track of Mega’s double CD album “Stereo”.', 'CTS Records представляет новый релиз от Sergio Mega. “Stereoland” – заглавный трек двухдискового CD альбома Sergio Mega - “Stereo”. ', './../images/274_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-28 14:14:45', '2009-04-24', 'yes', 'no', 57, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(275, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Sergio Mega - Stereo EP', 'Sergio Mega - Stereo EP', 'Continues Stereo project is also presented by Sergio Mega&rsquo;s &ldquo;Stereo EP&rdquo;. Compilation includes three full length tracks which were available before only at mixed CD, now in DJ friendly format. &ldquo;System One&rdquo; &ndash; album outro mix could finalize Techno &amp; Minimal set. Tech and pumping sound of &ldquo;Eraser&rdquo; combines with melodic Electro-Housy &ldquo;You&rdquo; which is made in Electronic-Rock instrumental manner. <br />', 'П', 'Continues Stereo project is also presented by Sergio Mega’s “Stereo EP”. ', 'Продолжающийся проект Stereo теперь представлен релизом “Stereo EP” от Sergio Mega', './../images/275_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:41:46', '2009-04-24', 'yes', 'no', 28, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(276, 0, 'releases', '', 'Sergio Mega - Stereo EP', 'CTS55093', '<br />', 'Sergio Mega -&nbsp;You&nbsp;(Instrumental)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Eraser<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;System One (Album Edit)', '', '27 April 2009', './../images/276_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-28 14:14:37', '2009-04-24', 'yes', 'no', 55, 'https://www.beatport.com/release/stereo-ep/168177', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/stereo-ep/168177', '', '', '&nbsp;', NULL),
(277, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CTSound EP vol.4 ', 'CTSound EP vol.4 ', 'New EP release from CTSound residents. Aquabeat shows juicy techno sound in &quot;Adrenaline&quot;. Ikiro comes with couple of his &quot;Psychoholic&quot; Progressive rhythms. Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde armed with their synthesizers are invited to join them at Minimal &quot;Elephant Hunt&quot;. Soon at CTS records new cool single release by Kotov &amp; Wilde - &quot;Ze Ozer Vang&quot; which includes remix from Techno specialist from Detroit - Anthony Attalla... Stay tuned...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nView <a target=\"\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;\" href=\"\\&quot;https://www.beatport.com/en-US/html/content/label/detail/4470/cts_creative_technologies_studio?bp_requested_content_type=html&amp;bp_requested_language=en-US&amp;labelId=4470&amp;labelName=cts_creative_technologies_studio&amp;pageNumber=1&amp;resultsPerPage=10#app=402a&amp;a486-index=0\\&quot;\">at Beatport</a> !<br />\r\n<a href=\"\\&quot;http://cts-label.com/mail/feedbackform/ctsoundep4/page.php\\&quot;\" target=\"\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;\"><br />\r\n</a>', 'Н', 'CTSound EP vol.4 released!', 'CTSound EP vol.4 вышел на Beatport!', './../images/277_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 14:33:45', '2009-05-15', 'yes', 'no', 14, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(278, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CTSound EP vol.5 (Different spring edit)', 'CTSound EP vol.5 (Different spring edit)', 'New streams in electronic music every time opens new horizons, Futura Partitura with &quot; Star Path&quot; plus Dunaewsky 69 with &quot;KosMarLunaPark&quot; and we have the sounds which shows modern, open minded views to Chill Out music. This Electronica &amp; Chill CTS Records Release also compiles lounge atmosphere in &quot;April Jam&quot; by Dan Brain and deep colors of &quot;Relax After Faxx&quot; by Ikiro... Nice for horizontal dancing, enjoy...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nView <a href=\"\\&quot;https://www.beatport.com/en-US/html/content/label/detail/4470/cts_creative_technologies_studio?bp_requested_content_type=html&amp;bp_requested_language=en-US&amp;labelId=4470&amp;labelName=cts_creative_technologies_studio&amp;pageNumber=1&amp;resultsPerPage=10#app=402a&amp;a486-index=0\\&quot;\" target=\"\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;\">at Beatport</a> !', 'Н', 'CTSound EP vol.5 (Different spring edit) released!\r\n', 'CTSound EP vol.5 (Different spring edit) вышел на Beatport!', './../images/278_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:53:55', '2009-05-15', 'yes', 'no', 19, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
