(282, 0, 'booking', 'no-alias', 'Storm Tarrion', 'Storm Tarrion', 'Storm Tarrion spawned from a troubled past growing up on the streets of Sydney Australia, you might say that his history led him to this point in time&hellip;. Music has always been a major part of his life, the most constant, it`s his driving passion. For the past ten years Adonaiiis has been writing heavily and composing original music in many forms. His style is unique and unlike any other, there are hints of rock, acid, electronic pop and old school house. The basis of his concept is to inspire the imagination and to make people listen a little closer, as there are many layers to his music. Storm understands that what is real and what is imagined is the same thing&hellip;.. After growing popularity, interest on the internet and some collaboration with other artists, now Storm already find a place to call home and to take things to a higher level - this is CTS records.', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '', '', './../images/282_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2011-05-16 14:15:13', '2009-05-20', 'yes', 'no', 289, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(283, 0, 'booking', 'no-alias', 'Niels von Geyer', 'Niels von Geyer', 'DJ Niels von Geyer, Berlin, plays a mixture of progressivehouse, pumpinhouse, vocalhouse, and classix, trance, electro. Ows a studio in Berlin together with his partner Mattias Harnos. As a dance music producer, his projects are Clubmossphere, Brotherhood of Sound, Disco Hools &amp; NVG. DJ Niels von Geyer works in Hamburg, Berlin and Moscow International publications and places in different dancecharts, mixed compilation THE ANNUAL for Ministry of Sound track at CLUBBERSGUIDE TO BERLIN (Ministry of Sound)&hellip;Remix Kate Ryan &hellip;Snap. He is signed to labels of Berlin-Phenomena, Clubmossphere, Germany, CTS (UA). Participates in different venues of Germany, Europe and worldwide - Loveparade, Lovestern Galactica, DJ-Meeting, Big Bang (Sweden), etc. In his non DJ-Life he is engaged in Extravadance - Radioshow at NRJ, Weiss der Geyer radio show, Eurotops, Dancehouse, Power Vision at the central German TV (ARD/ZDF). Also known as an actor (ZDF - serial &quot;During the next maneuver ...&quot;), free author for TV (LoopTV at Viva cannel), music journalist (Dates &amp; Tendance), music editor - [030] Berlin, DJ Promotion for Ministry of Sound (Germany), Kosmo, Great Stuff Recordings, Clubland, Sony /BMG.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore information at following websites:<br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.clubmossphere.de/\">www.clubmossphere.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.berlin-phenomena.de/\">www.berlin-phenomena.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.djpoolmos.clubmossphere.de/\">www.djpoolmos.clubmossphere.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.ministryofsound.de/\">www.ministryofsound.de</a>', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '', '', './../images/283_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2011-05-16 14:15:26', '2009-05-20', 'yes', 'no', 286, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(284, 0, 'booking', 'no-alias', 'Kotov & Andre Wilde', 'Kotov & Andre Wilde', 'DJ Kotov and Andre Wilde exploded onto the DJing scene in 2001. Their love for music and thirst for success led them to their place as one of the top DJ duos on the Toronto scene. They quickly attracted a following audience and secured a favourite position with their impeccable talent and vivacious vibes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWorking on the DJ scene and in LIVE projects with many well known artists. After big bang in The Guvernment club with famous Ferry Corsten, Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde makes cool performance together with Kaskade. Now is planned club project with resident of Super Star records &ndash; Tocadisco.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlaying in clubs of Montreal, Detroit, Miami, Chicago and New York as are Casa Blanca, The Docks, Cognac Lounge, The Guvernment, etc., Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde takes part in Electronic Music Open Air Festival in North America WEMF, Season 12. Now Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde makes their own sounds, run own club project &ldquo;VIP house&rdquo;, and have a credits at labels CTS records, Real Legacy records. They continue to bring us their scintillating music and extraordinary charisma while forging ahead onto new experiences.<br />', 'DJ Kotov и Andre Wilde ворвались на электронную сцену в 2001 году. Любовь к музыке и жажда успеха быстро утвердили их статус как одного из лучших DJ-дуэтов в Торонто. Они завоевали симпатии многих ценителей хорошей электронной музыки и заняли свою нишу среди канадских DJев благодаря таланту создавать живые, оригинальные ритмы.<br />\r\nВообще деятельность DJ Kotov и Andre Wilde иначе как бурной не назовешь. Они работали в сфере диджеинга и live-проектов со многими знаменитыми музыкантами.&nbsp; После взрывного выступления в клубе The Guvernment с Ferry Corsten создали бомбовый перформанс вместе с Kaskade, а так же совместного проект с резидентом Superstar recordings - Tocadisco в клубе Footwork.<br />\r\nДует постоянно играет в клубах Монреаля, Детройта, Майями, Чикаго и Нью-Йорка таких как: Casa Blanca, The Docks, Cognac Lounge, The Guvernment, в 2006 приняли приглашение участвовать в одном из самых знаменитых североамериканских Open Air - фестивалей WEMF (Session 12). На данный момент DJ Kotov и Andre Wilde активно создают новую музыку, работают над собственным клубным проектом \'VIP house\' и сотрудничают с лейблами Real Legacy records (USA), 4 Play Trax (Canada), Rawthentic (Canada), CTS records (Ukraine).<br />\r\nОни продолжают радовать нас своим искрометным битом и невероятной харизмой своих треков, никогда не останавливаясь на достигнутом в поисках новых музыкальных впечатлений!', '', '', './../images/284_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2011-05-23 13:34:37', '2009-05-20', 'yes', 'no', 293, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(285, 0, 'booking', 'no-alias', 'M.I.D.I.', 'M.I.D.I.', 'Music has been the biggest passion in M.I.D.I.&rsquo;s life and he shares that passion with other people since the tender age of 13. In the early days of his career, in the Nineties, Vito Laforge aka Dj M.I.D.I. played records at disco shows in Puglia and in the neighbouring regions where he began developing his techniques and cultivating his style. In summer of 2001, M.I.D.I. ruled the &ldquo;Heaven Island Fashion Priv&eacute;&rdquo; at DNA in Taranto working together with J.T. Vannelli, Ivan Iacobucci, Leo Mas, Massimiliano Beca, Lenny Fontana, Deepswing and other international top names. Among other disco clubs he worked at Theorema in Metaponto, Green Park in Adelfia, Merendero in Casamassima, Pasilda in Taranto and Silver System in Brindisi. He has been signed as a resident dj for &quot;House Innovative&quot; a famous event organiser&rsquo;s directory covering the south of Italy. His first release, &quot;Beats and peaces&quot;, in 2002, in collaboration with Costantino &ldquo;Mixmaster&rdquo; Padovano for &quot;M.I.D.I. Mix and Soul&quot; project, marked the beginning of his career as producer. His career culminates in 2006 with the project &ldquo;NARCOX&rdquo; in collaboration with singer-producer-dj Mowree. Their first release &quot;Kiss me back&quot;, for Python Records marked their debut, followed by the mixes &quot;Low G Call E.p. 01&quot; for Sugarshake Reloaded Records and &quot;Burnin\'&quot; for Soundivision Records. Among the others they have had production credits on labels like MOLTO RECORDS, DEEP DEEN RECORDS, V.O.T.U. RECORDS and CTS records. M.I.D.I. has taken part in the major international music gigs such as the Winter Music Conference 2003 in Miami, together with Chus &amp; Cheballos, Funky Junction, Marcello Castelli and Dr Love, the Street Rave Parade 2004 in Bologna together with Jayculture team and Francesco Farfa, Stefano Greppi, Ralf, Bruno Bolla and many other colleagues. Finally M.I.D.I. has actively collaborated in radio transmissions such as &quot;Master Groove&quot; on Radio Company Puglia in 2002 and &quot;Mastermind&quot; on Radioerre in 2004. Actually he takes part in the transmission &ldquo;Set for dj&rsquo;s&rdquo; on Dub Radio (Miami).<br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.djmidi.it/\">www.djmidi.it</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.myspace.com/mididj\">www.myspace.com/mididj</a>', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '', '', './../images/285_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2011-05-16 14:15:18', '2009-05-20', 'yes', 'no', 288, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL);
