(305, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'D\'mond - Announcement', 'D\'mond - Announcement', '<div style=\"\">CTS records present new single by DJ D&rsquo;mond &ndash; &ldquo;Announcement&rdquo;.  Techno release by master DJ from Portugal living in China. One of two Portuguese in top 200 DJ mag, became a key player in the development of Asian Club Scene. In the latest years his level of exposure, enabled him to team up with some of the industry icons, including Sasha, John Digweed, Derrick May, Nick Warren, James Zabiela, Lee Burridge, Chris Fortier, Anthony Pappa, Goldie&hellip;  One of the chill-out projects by D&rsquo;mond, Tchek Hoi Corp., was released on CTS last year. In 2009 on CTS &ldquo;Announcement&rdquo; get remixed by Green Grey DJ &ndash; Ekspert, Den Pleasure, Cyan Malkavian and DJ Fly.<br />\r\nRelease is supported by:  Lee Bradley (Central Recordings, UK), George G (Free Radio, Freeze Magazine, Greece), Greg Desty (Canada), Sergei Bitten (Ressonance, Mexico), DC (Vibe production, USA), Rickie Orion (Zen-Now, Canada), etc...<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<a target=\"\\\" href=\"\\\" http:=\"\" www.cts-label.com=\"\">Read Reviews </a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nView <a target=\"\\\" href=\"\\\" https:=\"\" www.beatport.com=\"\" en-us=\"\" html=\"\" content=\"\" label=\"\" detail=\"\">at Beatport</a> ! <br />', 'C', 'D\'mond - Announcement out on Beatport (27th of June)!', 'D\'mond - Announcement вышел на Beatport (27 Июня)!', './../images/305_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-29 13:59:18', '2009-07-01', 'yes', 'no', 38, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(306, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Aquarium EP', 'Aquarium EP', 'After successful release of &ldquo;Cocaine&rdquo;, which is still on the top of Kiss FM dance chart, new release by Aquabeat duo on CTS. &ldquo;Aquarium EP&rdquo; is personal point of view to summer techno and tech-house streams of Aquabeat project. Deep and trippy &ldquo;Magma&rdquo; with electro elements plus tech and minimal moods of &ldquo;Control of Emotions&rdquo; and you have two juicy tunes for the dancefloor.<br />', 'П', 'Aquarium EP out on Beatport (09th of June)!', 'Aquarium EP вышел на Beatport (09 Июня)!', './../images/306_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-08-01 13:22:51', '2009-07-01', 'yes', 'no', 33, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
