(318, 0, 'booking', 'no-alias', '2Sleepy', '2Sleepy', '2SLEEPY - &quot;bedroom pop&quot; band <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNadto Sonna (2sleepy) the electronica trio based in Kiev, Ukraine. After their debut &ldquo;Fragments Of Sleep&rdquo; was released on the Austrian label &lsquo;Laridae&rsquo; in 2006, the band gained a reputation of being the most interesting member of the independent Ukrainian pop-consortium. Audiences and critics warmly welcomed their second album &lsquo;Art Fraud&rsquo; (2008, ya-ok music), which was named one of the best albums of the year in the issue of &ldquo;Glavred&rdquo; magazine <br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Nadto Sonna&rdquo; participated in the international festival of experimental electronic music &ldquo;Detali Zvuku&rdquo;, performed gigs with the famous Russian cultural icon &ldquo;Dolphin&rdquo;, as well as with German electronica project &ldquo;SWOD&rdquo;.People in the band pay a lot of attention to their shows: they collaborate with various VJs to create a vibrant, memorable atmosphere. At concerts &ldquo;2sleepy&rdquo; play live, using the entire arsenal of their musical gear: synthesizers, samplers, effectors, and guitars. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n2sleepy is: Andriy Paranoid &ndash; programming, keyboard, drums, Yurko Dorialan - guitars, keyboards, Seva Soncev - vocal, programming, keyboards<br />', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '', '', './../images/318_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2011-05-16 14:15:04', '2009-07-23', 'yes', 'no', 291, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
