(322, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Ze Ozer Vang', 'Ze Ozer Vang', 'New release by Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde, duo from Toronto, Canada on CTS records. After successful &ldquo;Smasher EP&rdquo; which reached Canadian top 40, leaved behind tracks by such stars as Britney Spears and neighboring with Fedde Le Grand, Kotov &amp; Wilde coming up with &ldquo;Ze Ozer Vang&rdquo;. Techno and House sounds are tightly matched in this dynamic release. Tech and House original mix with melodic breakdown - dancefloor burner! Modern Tech sounds are represented by Anthony Attalla from Detroit. Master of turn tables and new wave techno producer reminded again by his remix that Detroit is a motherland of Techno music. Club colored Tech-House remix by Sergio Mega add European moods to the release.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nView <a target=\"_blank\"  href=\"https://www.beatport.com/en-US/html/content/release/detail/181259/Ze%20Ozer%20Vang\">at Beatport</a> ! <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.cts-label.com/reviews.html\">Read Reviews </a>', 'Н', 'Ze Ozer Vang out on Beatport (15th of July)!', 'Ze Ozer Vang вышел на Beatport (15 Июля)!', './../images/322_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-29 13:59:06', '2009-07-28', 'yes', 'no', 35, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
(323, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CTSound EP vol.6', 'CTSound EP vol.6', 'Next CTSound EP combines different shades of Techo, House and Electro. Included dj friendly club mix of Lamineylf&rsquo;s &ldquo;Algat&rdquo;, animals sounded project of well known Ukrainian electronic musician Dunaewsky 69. Actifish continue his sea theme with, electrified progressive melodic forms in track &ldquo;Black Sea&rdquo;. In volume 6 of CTSound EP edition we are welcome Ukrainian newcomers &ndash; Crime Project duo with Electro Housy &ldquo;Dead Eyes&rdquo; and Roman Sweet with Techno track &ldquo;Head Shot&rdquo;, enjoy&hellip;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nView <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.beatport.com/en-US/html/content/label/detail/4470/cts_creative_technologies_studio?bp_requested_content_type=html&amp;bp_requested_language=en-US&amp;labelId=4470&amp;labelName=cts_creative_technologies_studio&amp;pageNumber=1&amp;resultsPerPage=10#app=402a&amp;a486-index=0\">at Beatport</a> !<br />\r\n<br />', 'С', 'CTSound EP vol.6 out on Beatport (27th of July)!', 'CTSound EP vol.6 вышел на Beatport (27 Июля)!', './../images/323_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-29 13:59:11', '2009-07-28', 'yes', 'no', 36, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
