(328, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CTSound EP vol.7', 'CTSound EP vol.7', 'Next monthly brand compilation from CTS records. &ldquo;Candle&rdquo; - Techno with deep synth line by Justy, dark and trippy. Minimalistic, Tech grooves in Cyan Malkavian&rsquo;s &ldquo;Tookietoo&rdquo;, pumping sounds for body moving. Electrified Tech-House remix by Crime Project to the track &ldquo;Head Shot&rdquo; from Roman Sweet reached #2 position in Releasepromo Electro Chart and get to the TOP 50 Hipe Chart . <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img width=\"\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\&quot;\" height=\"\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&quot;\\\\&quot;\\&quot;\" src=\"/images/Electro_Chart_small470.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nDance, dance, dance&hellip;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCTSound EP vol.7 is supported by: Bitten Sergei (Mexico), Edge Howk (Voodoo Lounge, EnSonic.fm Radio, USA), George G (Free Radio 98.00, Freeze magazine, Greece), DJ Science (Science &amp; Reason, Canada), DJ Mindaugelis (Audio Therapy, Lithuania) etc... <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.beatport.com/en-US/html/content/release/detail/188780/CTSound%20EP%20Volume%207\">Download from Beatport!</a><br />\r\n<br />', 'Н', 'CTSound EP vol.7 is available on Beatport!', 'CTSound EP vol.7 уже доступен для скачивания на  Beatport!', './../images/328_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-29 13:55:11', '2009-09-02', 'yes', 'no', 39, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(329, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Ikiro – Without You', 'Ikiro – Without You', 'New single by Ikiro, originally is the main track in the debut album by Ukrainian producer. Deep House feelings are mainly in the release, made by Ikiro includes Original mix, Vocal mix and the Remix. For Electro-House lovers best one is a remix by Daniel Ost. Vocals by Julia Dzidziguri from Georgia are velvet and guitar by Russian musician Eugene Larin is going through the track.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.beatport.com/en-US/html/content/release/detail/187474/Without%20You\">Download from Beatport!</a><br />\r\n<br />', 'Н', '\"Ikiro – Without You\" starts on Beatport!', 'Ikiro – Without You стартует на Beatport!', './../images/329_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-29 13:56:02', '2009-09-02', 'yes', 'no', 42, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(330, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'CTSound Podcast vol.3', 'CTSound Podcast vol.3', 'August podcast from CTS records is marked as &ldquo;Funky mix&rdquo;. Made by really funky musician, CTS resident and Green Grey staff DJ &ndash; Ekspert&hellip; enjoy and be funky!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.cts-label.com/podcast.html\">Download Podcast!</a><br />', 'А', 'CTSound Podcast vol.3 - DJ Ekspert Funky Mix is available for downloading!', 'CTSound Podcast vol.3 - DJ Ekspert Funky Mix доступен для скачивания!', './../images/330_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-29 13:17:20', '2009-09-02', 'yes', 'no', 44, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(331, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Sergey Lazarev a.k.a. Sergio Mega - «Joe Dassin In The House»', 'Сергей Лазарев а.k.а. Sergio Mega – «Joe Dassin In The House»', '<br />\r\nA new look at the evergreen hit by Joe Dassin &laquo;Indian summer&raquo; (L\\\\\\\'Ete Indien) from the Ukrainian DJ and producer Sergei Lazarev aka Sergio Mega. Colorful, Club House sound gave a new charm to the well-known tune; the vocals in a cover version were performed by Rita Lake and Sergey Lazarev. <br />\r\nThe fame and popularity came to Joe Dassin in May 1975, when his producer heard an Italian composition that had been sung in English by a group &laquo;Albatross&raquo;. It was called &laquo;Africa&raquo;; the author of the music was, as the press had been writing then, - &laquo;a certain Toto Cutugno&raquo;, and the author of words - Vito Pallavicini, who was better known in French musical circles. <br />\r\nJust that very composition is the work that will form the basis of the famous &laquo;L \\\\\\\'Ete indien&raquo;, that was sung by Dassin and has brought to him the real fame... <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"\\&quot;http://www.cts-label.com/2/sound/joedassin/Sergey_Lazarev_aka_Sergio_Mega_-_Joe_Dassin_In_The_House_(Original_Cut).mp3\\&quot;\">Listen track</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nSergey Lazarev a.k.a. Sergio Mega - &laquo;Joe Dassin In The House&raquo;<br />\r\n(c) УМИГ, 2009<br />\r\n(p) CTS, 2009<br />\r\n<br />', '<div><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">CTS</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">records</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \"> представляет</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Новая версия мирового хита Джо Дассен &laquo;Бабье Лето&raquo;</span></div>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div><b><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Сергей</span></b><b><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Лазарев</span></b><b><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">а</span></b><b><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">.k.</span></b><b><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">а</span></b><b><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">. Sergio Mega &ndash; &laquo;Joe Dassin In The House&raquo;</span></b></div>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<div style=\"&quot;text-align: \"><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Новый взгляд на хит всех времен Джо Дассен &laquo;Бабье Лето&raquo; (</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">L</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">&rsquo;</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Ete</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Indien</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">) от украинского </span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">DJ</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \"> и продюсера Сергея Лазарева </span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">a</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">.</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">k</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">.</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">a</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">. </span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Sergio</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Mega</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">. Колоритный, клубный </span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">House</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \"> саунд придал известной мелодии новый шарм, вокальные партии в кавер-версии исполнили Rita Lake и Сергей Лазарев. </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"&quot;text-align: \"><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Известность и популярность пришла к Джо Дассену в мае 1975 года, когда его продюсер услышал итальянское произведение, спетое по-английски группой &laquo;Альбатрос&raquo;. Оно называлось &laquo;Африка&raquo;, автором музыки был, как писала тогда пресса, - &laquo;некто Тото Кутуньо&raquo;, а автором слов &ndash; более известный во французских музыкальных кругах Вито Паллавичини.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Именно это произведение ляжет в основу знаменитой &laquo;L \\\'Еte indien&raquo;, спетой Дассеном и принесшей ему славу&hellip;</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \"><a href=\"\\&quot;http://www.cts-label.com/2/sound/joedassin/Sergey_Lazarev_aka_Sergio_Mega_-_Joe_Dassin_In_The_House_(Original_Cut).mp3\\&quot;\">Прослушать трек</a></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Сергей</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">Лазарев</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">а</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">.k.</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">а</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">. Sergio Mega &ndash; &laquo;Joe Dassin In The House&raquo;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">(c) УМИГ</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">, 2009</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"&quot;font-size: \">(p) CTS, 2009</span></div>', 'CTS records presents: A new version of the world hit Joe Dassin «Indian Summer»', 'CTS records представляет: Новая версия мирового хита Джо Дассен «Бабье Лето»\r\n', './../images/331_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-29 13:55:22', '2009-09-02', 'yes', 'no', 40, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
