(695, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Aquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Ride The Time', 'Aquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Ride The Time', 'After big and cool &ldquo;Cocaine&rdquo; release Aquabeat is back with new mass single &ldquo;Ride the Time&rdquo;. Traditionally vocals by Kiss FM voice - Rey-Na. Sounds get us to the future,  first part of the release includes original mix, remixes by well known Brazilian producer Truati, from Canadian duo Kotov&amp;Andre Wilde and Tech-House remix by Sergio Mega. Second part of the release is planed to January 2010. <br />', 'П', 'Aquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Ride The Time coming to Beatport soon!', 'Aquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Ride The Time скоро на Beatport!', './../images/695_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-28 14:14:16', '2009-12-30', 'yes', 'no', 53, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL),
