(1367, 0, 'news', 'no-alias', 'Sergio Mega @ Ministry Of Sound Radio', 'Sergio Mega @ Ministry Of Sound Radio', 'Niels von Geyer, the Ministry Of Sound (Berlin) resident, presents the brand-new and the hottest tracks from the world of electronic music. Sunshine Live Radio and Ministry Of Sound cooperation has created a perfect platform for high-quality dance music from the whole world. Niels von Geyer presents in his two-hour show the best House, Electro and Progressive sounds. Every week exclusive DJ mix from famous artists such as David Guetta, Bob Sinclar, Stonebrige, Eric Pridz, Mousse T and many others go on the air!  Radio show from Ministry of Sound is an acoustic firework of superior-quality!<br />\r\nSergio Mega presents his hot newest set of groovy and Tech-House tunes selected specially for Ministry of Sound Radio Show in July 2011.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://soundcloud.com/cts-records/sergio-mega-special-dj-mix\">Listen/comment/download @ SoundCloud</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nTracklist:<br />\r\n1. Artur Grek &ndash; Jamal (Intro Mix) [CTS Records]<br />\r\n2. Taco Man &amp; Jose M &ndash; The World is Yours (Original Mix) [The Room Records]<br />\r\n3. Sergio Mega &ndash; Upper (Original Mix) [CTS Records]<br />\r\n4. Alex Kenji &ndash; Wekesa (DJ PP Remix) [303Lovers/Hotfingers]<br />\r\n5. Alexander Fog &ndash; House in South Beach (Original Mix) [TMR Records]<br />\r\n6. Green Velvet &ndash; Flash (Channel X Remix) [Relief Records]<br />\r\n7. Bass Kleph &ndash; I&rsquo;ll Be Ok (Superskank Remix) [Definitive Recordings]<br />\r\n8. Format B &ndash; Gospel (Super Flu&rsquo;s Antichrist Remix) [DJ Exklusive (Vidisco) Records]<br />\r\n9. Taco Man &amp; Jose M &ndash; Tom Collins (Original Mix) [The Room]<br />\r\n10. As Brain &ndash; Water (Original Mix) [Attari Records]<br />\r\n11. Hector Couto &ndash; Mareme (DJ PP Remix) [Gramma Records]<br />\r\n<br />', 'Резидент Ministry Of Sound (Berlin) &ndash; Niels Von Geyer презентуе