(1612, 0, 'releases', 'new', 'Sergio Mega - Ornamental (the Album)', 'CTS260143', 'The third album of Sergio Mega &quot;Ornamental&quot; comes out in the spring of 2014. Name of the album consists of two volumetric components, which means Ornament - DNA of the nation and Mentality - the soul of the nation. The release concept is coupled global authentic culture and modern electronic music. The project includes eleven audio pieces; each one is based on musical traditions from around the world, combining their rich texture with rhythmic electronic instruments and synthesizers. Remixes for the album tracks except Ukrainian sound producers already made by the artists from the United States, Spain, Argentina, Germany, Malta, Italy, the Netherlands and Mexico as well. The main objective of the project show colors Ukrainian musical culture an integral part of the global palette ornament. As a result, the integration of Ukrainian electronic sound into the flow of international contemporary electronic music.', 'Sergio Mega -&nbsp;Opening (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Vagator&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Stereoland (Ornamental Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Upper&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega &nbsp;- Carnaval (Album Version)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Gogol&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Kyiv Skies&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Mystic &amp; Wilde (Album Version)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Deeper Dnieper&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega feat. Jean Osoa&nbsp;-&nbsp;In Motion (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Beat On The Drums&nbsp;(Original Mix)', '', '21 March 2014', './../images/1612_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2016-05-18 15:40:40', '2014-03-17', 'yes', 'no', 260, 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sergio-mega-ornamental-the-album/1269124', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', '', '', NULL, NULL),
