(1818, 0, 'releases', '', 'Filya Trevelyan - Monotraks EP', 'CTS336173', 'We are happy to welcome Finnish DJ &amp; producer Filya Trevelyan with his debut EP on CTS. 3 brand new techno tracks all shows different sides of techno. All tracks are trippy with a gradually unfolding plot, &quot;Autumn&quot; is dark and dirty,&nbsp;atmospheric &quot;404&quot; and another one is faster - &quot;Chicago&quot; with strong and tight groove.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSupported by:<br />\r\nPK Live (Garage Club, Festival Synergy, Brazil),&nbsp;DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, Scene, Niketalk Magazine, USA),&nbsp;Maurizio Santi (Promotionalrecord, Modena Radio City, Radio Mela, Gonnosfanadiga, Italy),&nbsp;Markus Baumhackl (NiteFlight, Austria),&nbsp;DJ Trouble (Foo bar, Italy),&nbsp;DJ DiRRty HaRRi (Sonic Music Prod, 2 Tone Music, Tony &amp; Adam&#39;s, Thunder Bay, Canada), &nbsp;DJ Lothar (Der Gardinen-Service, Shagall, Germany),&nbsp;RIshi Bass (Sound of Music, Netherlands), DJ Lakey (ADSR Records, USA),&nbsp;Jayson Butera (Elliptical Sun, VIM Recordings, USA), Bryant LittleJhon (Global Vibes Mixshow, USA),&nbsp;Linda Leigh (Technotica, Burst Radio Detroit and EJR Radio Amsterdam, USA) and many more...<a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read reviews</a>', '<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=24HB5Hwf5yQ&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;index=18\">Filya Trevelyan - Autumn</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XYSjJ_QEku4&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;index=17\">Filya Trevelyan - Chicago</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=stg5j9AJIHU&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;index=16\">Filya Trevelyan - 404</a>', '', ' 8 September 2017', './../images/1818_s.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2018-02-23 16:03:06', '2017-08-31', 'yes', 'no', 336, 'https://www.beatport.com/release/monotraks-ep/2104470', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=24HB5Hwf5yQ&index=18&t=0s&list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp', '', '', 'Рњ